  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nAs described in https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/11376 passing amounts between ui and backend is unreliable and may lead to distortions. In https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/11491 it's refactored for minting, airdropping and burning. Similar refactor should be done for permissions.\r\n\r\nIt should also fix current problems with displaying decimal fractions provided by the user:\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2023-08-10 16-06-30](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/20650004/38390d56-b818-449e-8221-78d45d7a3015)\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2023-08-10 16-06-50](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/20650004/08f296cb-249e-498d-95bd-b48e368f28d8)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
